{"id": "ChIJBSIlkmyVj4ARn8bt0wJCURI", "rating": 4.7, "userRatingCount": 199, "displayName": {"text": "Doughweime Bakery & Café", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJBSIlkmyVj4ARn8bt0wJCURI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxblZXRXhjR1pYZUZKRVF6UldkelZ1UW1kZmRFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Best malasada in town with very unique flavors. The dough is soft and the cream is light, but the price is pretty steep with each one being  $6.50+. Good thing I love far from them because otherwise my wallet will be hurting. With a all the unique flavors, itsy hard not to try more than one. I do love that they have the option of mini malasadas so you can eat even more without being too filled from each one. Everytime I go, there's always something new so it's a nice surprise each visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Best malasada in town with very unique flavors. The dough is soft and the cream is light, but the price is pretty steep with each one being  $6.50+. Good thing I love far from them because otherwise my wallet will be hurting. With a all the unique flavors, itsy hard not to try more than one. I do love that they have the option of mini malasadas so you can eat even more without being too filled from each one. Everytime I go, there's always something new so it's a nice surprise each visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Deanna Leung", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104162231475585321930/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7YmutJgAcIUnl3Vc1qrrZ3GGuT22gBU5NVSsWlzBnN3E-lVlScg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-25T15:10:54.686509783Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxblZXRXhjR1pYZUZKRVF6UldkelZ1UW1kZmRFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxblZXRXhjR1pYZUZKRVF6UldkelZ1UW1kZmRFRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f956c92252205:0x12514202d3edc69f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBSIlkmyVj4ARn8bt0wJCURI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toNE1YVkVMVlY0VkdkTGNsTkpSa1YyVWxKS2RYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Doughweime has some incredible malasadas as well as other pastries like crossaints! They're always showcasing unique flavors, many of which my partner and I tried and enjoyed. The s'mores, black sesame, and ube malasadas were some of our favorites! Highly recommend checking them out 🙌🏼", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Doughweime has some incredible malasadas as well as other pastries like crossaints! They're always showcasing unique flavors, many of which my partner and I tried and enjoyed. The s'mores, black sesame, and ube malasadas were some of our favorites! Highly recommend checking them out 🙌🏼", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brooke C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104376127720964209451/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVN8FnSh6n40dY9m433frY80D5NH3WxCYYCnj1-UiVXDXWYgb6PYg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-22T21:40:07.663661369Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toNE1YVkVMVlY0VkdkTGNsTkpSa1YyVWxKS2RYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toNE1YVkVMVlY0VkdkTGNsTkpSa1YyVWxKS2RYYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f956c92252205:0x12514202d3edc69f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBSIlkmyVj4ARn8bt0wJCURI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WMU1tTmtjRGg2WjJkMlJuZ3pXVzU1YlVkbkxYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Arguably one of the best bakeries in the bay! High quality ingredients and very creative donut flavors, it’s worth making a trip just to stop by here.\n\nThe coffee is good too! I’ve been to a few cafes that either have good food or good drinks, you don’t have to worry about that here", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Arguably one of the best bakeries in the bay! High quality ingredients and very creative donut flavors, it’s worth making a trip just to stop by here.\n\nThe coffee is good too! I’ve been to a few cafes that either have good food or good drinks, you don’t have to worry about that here", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sarah", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113818198177118525294/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYTW3fuMsMxzueBvBMr43QD7iV9G8UcUK5iEUfqmYv74nqJw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-03T01:28:59.963014677Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WMU1tTmtjRGg2WjJkMlJuZ3pXVzU1YlVkbkxYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WMU1tTmtjRGg2WjJkMlJuZ3pXVzU1YlVkbkxYYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f956c92252205:0x12514202d3edc69f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBSIlkmyVj4ARn8bt0wJCURI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5R1QyMW9RaTFHT0ZaUWVsaHFRM1J6U3pWSFdGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place has it all! Wonderful, kind service. AMAZING malasadas with rotating, creative flavors. Seriously, everything is always so well balanced, fresh, and not too sweet. I could go on and on about how much I love the baked goods here. My only tip is to go early (especially on the weekends) if there are specific flavors you want.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place has it all! Wonderful, kind service. AMAZING malasadas with rotating, creative flavors. Seriously, everything is always so well balanced, fresh, and not too sweet. I could go on and on about how much I love the baked goods here. My only tip is to go early (especially on the weekends) if there are specific flavors you want.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christine C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105593449058789391083/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIe5DR_ppsCi3KtID7oLt49ZXeRTd3tZkEj10A5TG8wBKSjYg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-07T21:23:47.801257291Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5R1QyMW9RaTFHT0ZaUWVsaHFRM1J6U3pWSFdGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5R1QyMW9RaTFHT0ZaUWVsaHFRM1J6U3pWSFdGRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f956c92252205:0x12514202d3edc69f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJBSIlkmyVj4ARn8bt0wJCURI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21zeFVERkRkMHhEWm04MWNuVm1hVmgwZEU5V1dXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Nama donuts are yummy! They're uniquely soft, fluffy and chewy, think mochi cloud consistency. Have to try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Nama donuts are yummy! They're uniquely soft, fluffy and chewy, think mochi cloud consistency. Have to try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Andy Nougat", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113514956317015029883/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDA1xaG1FxzfoFbgKMZoK75WDalu-c7rHtJ7gAXERij1leX0Zd5A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-30T21:48:32.876630483Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21zeFVERkRkMHhEWm04MWNuVm1hVmgwZEU5V1dXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21zeFVERkRkMHhEWm04MWNuVm1hVmgwZEU5V1dXYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f956c92252205:0x12514202d3edc69f"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJBSIlkmyVj4ARn8bt0wJCURI/photos/